{"title": "Flexible work arrangements can\u2019t be for just well-paid professionals", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2023-10-12", "content": "Shorter work week, longer parental leave, flexibility for new parents and caregivers \u2013 there is currently strong emphasis on flexi-work and work-life balance.\nIn Singapore, a tripartite workgroup has been formed to develop flexi-work arrangements (FWAs), including flexi-time, flexi-place and flexi-workload."}